mooth delivery of intricate 3D content.\n\uff0eCustomizable Avatars and Interactive Features: Personalize your virtual presence and engage in interactive discussions effortlessly.\n\uff0eEnterprise-Grade Security and Privacy: Rest assured with VIVERSE for Business's robust security measures, safeguarding your data and privacy at every step.\n\uff0eSeamless Integration: Access your immersive environments seamlessly, ensuring connectivity regardless of location, including on Oculus devices.\n \nWhy Choose VIVERSE for Business:\n\uff0eEnhanced Productivity and Engagement: Empower your team with tools that elevate productivity, connectivity, and engagement within immersive environments.\n\uff0eCompliance and Reliability: VIVERSE for Business adheres to industry regulations and standards, backed by reliable infrastructure and continuous support.\n\nDownload VIVERSE for Business now and unlock the potential of immersive collaboration for your organization.\n", "short_description": "VIVERSE for Business provides immersive and collaborative solution"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.htc.com/us/terms/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://service.viverse.com/hc/article_attachments/19518290360333", "publisher_name": "VIVERSE Limited.", "support_website_url": "https://service.viverse.com/hc/en-us/requests/new", "website_url": "https://www.viverse.com/business", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "SITTING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "